    <h2>Chapter 4: Joseph – Prophecy Meets Process</h2>
    <blockquote>“Until the time came to fulfill his dreams, the LORD tested Joseph’s character.” — Psalm 105:19 (NLT)</blockquote>
    <p>Of all biblical figures, Joseph embodies the tension between prophecy and process…</p>
    <div class="scripture"><h3>Scripture Meditation:</h3><ul><li>Genesis 37:5–11</li><li>Genesis 39–41</li><li>Psalm 105:19</li></ul></div>
</section>

