    <h2>Chapter 9: Delays Are Not Denials</h2>
    <blockquote>“For the vision awaits its appointed time; it hastens to the end—it will not lie. If it seems slow, wait for it; it will surely come; it will not delay.” — Habakkuk 2:3</blockquote>
